Code Information
The MATLAB script implements the complete anomaly detection pipeline, including:
•	Dataset loading and consolidation
•	Missing value handling
•	Separation of normal and patient instances
•	Variance-based filter feature selection
•	Three-dimensional feature visualization
•	Adaptive parameter estimation for DBSCAN clustering
•	Density-based clustering and anomaly identification
•	Quantitative performance evaluation
•	Comparative analysis with baseline classifiers
Custom functions required in the MATLAB path:
•	DBSCAN
•	PlotClusterinResult
•	KNN
•	SVM
•	NN
•	DT
•	NB
